{{champion:157}} 

He's not a champion.  Nothing with a design this cancerous deserves to be called one.  I don't care how "underpowered" or "balanced" Yasuo seems to others with the extreme amount of changes this _thing_ has received since it infected our client.  Until the rework, this is one of the worst ideas to put on the roster and leave alone without further kit alterations, and this type of design is praised by Riot....why?? 

in what universe is this fun to play against?  Why is recourcless and 30 passives a good idea?? What the fuck is Wind Wall a product of; meth, crack, or complete idiocy? I'd throw Ekko in here because of similar problems, but I believe Gypsylord has a degree of humility and sympathy for people who have to play against his kits, or Kalista - but I think everyone still hates the kangaroo.

{{champion:35}} 

He's so popular and I hate it. Playing against him is a nightmare, and even when you're technically winning against him you can't even catch him. 
IMO he's a champ designed by trolls for trolls for the purpose of trolling and making lives miserable.

The. Fucking. Donger.

{{champion:74}} 
Try to get close to him? LOL Here's some turret shots. The ONLY way to get him? Range with vel or xerath. Annihilate from afar :D (but even playing as a counter is still SO ANNOYING)
